child.name: numberOfMembers
child.description:
This attribute identifies the total number of TPs or GTPs currently contained in the TPPool.

This attribute has multiplicity 0..1

This attribute is optional
child.label: numberOfMembers

child.name: numberOfIdleMembers
child.description:
This attribute identifies the number of currently contained idle TPs or GTPs in the TPPool.

This attribute has multiplicity 0..1

This attribute is optional
child.label: numberOfIdleMembers

child.name: commonTransmissionParameterList
child.description:
This attribute contains the common layers and Transmission Parameters associated with the TPs grouped by the associated TpPool (or contained by the GTPs that are grouped by the associated TPPool). Refer to attached supporting document SD1-16_LayeredParameters for details of the currently defined Transmission Parameters.

This attribute has multiplicity *

This attribute is optional
child.label: commonTransmissionParameterList

child.name: descriptionOfUse
child.description:
This attribute contains a description of the specific use of the TPPool. The description of use of an ATM VP TPPool would be "VirtualUNI", if all its VP CTPs are contained in the same real user network interface (UNI) (i.e., a tributary ATM NI CTP) that is partitioned into virtual UNIs (i.e., VP TPPools).

This attribute has multiplicity 0..1

This attribute is optional
child.label: descriptionOfUse
